- ui_name = LinkedData.settings.ui_name
%p
  A new project has been created on 
  %b #{ui_name}:
%div{style: "background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #{Notifier::PORTAL_COLOR}; margin: 20px 0;"}
  %p{style: "margin: 0 0 10px 0;"}
    %strong Acronym: 
    = context[:acronym]
  %p{style: "margin: 0 0 10px 0;"}
    %strong Name: 
    = context[:name]
%p
  Access it here:
  %a{href: "#{context[:proj_url]}"}= "#{context[:proj_url]}"
%p
  You are receiving this notification because you are subscribed to new projects.
